<div class='inputInstr Small'>
	To look up scriptures that inspired the Lord's date for Armageddon, 
	set the date on the controls below and tap <b>Scriptures</b>.
</div>


<div id=inputWrapper>
	<div id=inputs >
		<table >
			<tr>
				<td colspan=2 style='text-align:center; '>Armageddon is on</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style='text-align:right; '>date:</td>
				<td><select name=date id=date >
					<option value=any>any</option>
					<script>
						for (var d = 1; d <= 31; d++)
							document.write("  <option value="+ d +">"+ d +"</option>\n");
					</script>
				</select>
				</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style='text-align:right; '>month:</td>
				<td><select name=month id=month>
					<option value=any>any month</option>
					<option value=3>March</option>
					<option value=4>April</option>
					<option value=5>May</option>
					<option value=6>June</option>
					<option value=7>July</option>
					<option value=8>August</option>
					<option value=9>September</option>
					<option value=10>October</option>
					<option value=11>November</option>
					<option value=12>December</option>
					<option value=1>January</option>
					<option value=2>February</option>
				</select></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style='text-align:right; '>year:</td>
				<td><input name=year id=year size=10 ></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td></td>
				<td><button type='button' id=justify>Scriptures</button></td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	
		{{! this image has color #ddb980 in the middle of it }}
		<img id=inputScroll src=flatscroll.png onmousedown=event.preventDefault() >
	</div>
</div>

<div class='inputInstr Large'>
	<div>
	Now, YOU can augment the credibility of God's foretelling about the end of days.  Steps:
	</div>
	<ul>
		<li>• <b>Enter the date</b> God has given you that Armageddon is on</li>
		<li>• Click <b>Scriptures</b></li>
		<li>• Dial-a-Geddon will retrieve several formulas of <b>Biblical scriptures</b> that may explain the date.  We recommend you choose verses that are consonant with your recent sermons.</li>
	</ul>
</div>

